 So I imagine that at some point there was this primordial

11:35.720 --> 11:40.720
 soup of amino acids and maybe some proteins in the ocean.

11:41.320 --> 11:44.840
 And some proteins were turning into some other proteins

11:44.840 --> 11:46.360
 through reaction.

